{"tid":2280012,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"再有foodpanda外賣員炒車，遭違例轉彎的士撞低","createTime":"2020-11-10T07:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T07:40:32.000Z","uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a002b8a69e2005aaba3fc842e20dacf878227cff","tid":2280012,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T07:40:32.000Z","msg":"再有foodpanda外賣員遇交通意外。下午1時左右，foodpanda外賣員駕駛電單車沿旺角洗衣街北行往花墟方向，至弼街交界，對面線的士疑違例轉入弼街，結果將電單車撞倒。外賣員人仰馬翻，受傷倒在地上，多名途人及其他駕駛者上前協助，傷者稍後由救護車送院治理。的士司機姓陳59歲，警方正就意外展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n傷者姓湛50歲，手腳受傷送廣華醫院治理。傷者妻子接報後趕到醫院，她指丈夫是foodpanda的全職員工，入職多年，她暫時未知意外原因，但引述現場人士稱是對方司機違規。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y6t0WPh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy6t0WPh.png&h=ee3454ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n的士疑違例右轉弼街，結果撞倒往花墟方向的電單車，鐵騎士倒在地上等候救援。<br />\n<br />\n內有更詳盡事發經過<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201110/OW54PBQ3MRCYVGJE3MKCYPOJEM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201110%2FOW54PBQ3MRCYVGJE3MKCYPOJEM%2F&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7Igg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=bb05b782\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201110%2FOW54PBQ3MRCYVGJE3MKCYPOJEM%2F&h=bab20db6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201110/OW54PBQ3MRCYVGJE3MKCYPOJEM/</a>"}]}